Class CommonProjectService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appinventor.server.project.CommonProjectService
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    YoungAndroidProjectService

    public abstract class CommonProjectService
extends Object
    The base class for classes that provide project services for a specific project type.

      • load

        public String load(String userId,
          long projectId,
          String fileId)
        Loads the file information associated with a node in the project tree. The actual return value depends on the file kind. Source (text) files should typically return their contents. Image files will be more likely to return the URL that the browser can find them at.
        Parameters:
        userId - the user id
        projectId - project root node ID
        fileId - project node whose source should be loaded
        Returns:
        implementation dependent

        Invokes a build command for the project.

        build results

      • getBuildResult

        public abstract RpcResult getBuildResult(User user,
                       long projectId,
                       String target)
        Gets the result of a build command for the project.
        Parameters:
        user - the User that owns the projectId.
        projectId - project id to be built
        target - build target (optional, implementation dependent.
        Returns:
        build results. The following values may be in RpcResult.result: 0: Build is done and was successful 1: Build is done and was unsuccessful -1: Build is not yet done.
